WEBVTT

00:04:29.605 --> 00:04:31.906
and to keep people tuned to the TV.

00:04:33.962 --> 00:04:39.353
Do you recall a particular image of me,
say, wearing a beret?

00:04:41.480 --> 00:04:44.084
Now, I admit I made mistakes --

00:04:44.108 --> 00:04:46.254
especially wearing that beret.

00:04:46.278 --> 00:04:48.204
(Laughter)

00:04:48.228 --> 00:04:50.890
But the attention and judgment
that I received --

00:04:50.914 --> 00:04:54.237
not the story, but that
I personally received --

00:04:54.261 --> 00:04:55.821
was unprecedented.

00:04:56.713 --> 00:04:59.163
I was branded as a tramp,